        {
          "id": "page-4-source-fatrah",
          "kind": "scholarly_annotation",
          "title": {
            "ar": "فترة الوحي",
            "en": "The pause in revelation (Fatrah)"
          },
          "scholar": {
            "ar": "ابن حجر العسقلاني",
            "en": "Ibn Hajar al-Asqalani"
          },
          "work": {
            "ar": "فتح الباري",
            "en": "Fath al-Bari"
          },
          "note": {
            "ar": "يوضح ابن حجر أن فترة الوحي كانت لحكمة ترويض النبي ﷺ وتهيئته نفسياً لحمل الرسالة بعد المفاجأة الأولى.",
            "en": "Ibn Hajar explains that the pause in revelation served the wisdom of acclimatizing the Prophet ﷺ and preparing him psychologically to bear the message after the initial surprise."
          },
